1 brokerage firm, or company registered under the Investment Company Act of
2 1940, 15 U.S.C. § 80a-1, et seq., and designate the State or the appropriate
3 permitting agency as the beneficiary. The Department may specify the form
4 in which the bond or set-aside funds are provided, as well as a procedure for
5 transfer of the financial assurance if ownership of the upland basin marina
6 changes."
